modName: Brokefoot UNP Mashup Compilation UNPB BBP BBPx Conversion
summary:
This is a conversion of the TOPs for Brokefoot UNP Mashup Compilation to UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx It requires Brokefoot's original mod. This is only Mesh and weight changes for the UNPB body type. Working weight slider.
UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx Body Replacers for Temptress Race users in miscellaneous
descriptionHtml:
This is a conversion of the TOPs for Brokefoot UNP Mashup Compilation for UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx It requires Brokefoot's original mod. This is only Mesh and weight changes for the UNPB body type. Working weight slider.

Install Brokefoot's mod first [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20415]Brokefoot UNP Mashup Compilation[/url] then overwrite the files for the body type you want.

There is a main file For those who do NOT use the Temptress Race, and an Optional file For those who DO use the Temptress Race. Choose one or the other, not both.

If there are any issues let me know, and which version/top you are using. Thanks!

Added

UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx Body Replacers for Temptress Race users in miscellaneous.
This is just a repackage for ease of install of the two mesh files (femalebody_0.nif femalebody_1.nif). The original is on the UNPB page, or Dimons' UNP page (my conversion from my Barkeeper mod page).
You can get SFW Chainmail textures from
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45]Obligatory Chainmail Bikini by Rekicker[/url]
Or HD textures from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23875]High Definition Undergarments UNP UNPB by crispiniscool[/url]
another [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24747]High Definition Leather Undergarments by crispiniscool[/url]
or use the texture from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709]dimon99's SFW bikinis[/url]
